{"type": "article", "id": 26907, "title": "弯曲的衣架", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-17T06:45:31Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 41, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021157376zxCycpQNAYadW9I.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>千篇一律的衣架造型是不是已经让你感到厌烦了？丹麦设计双人组 GamFratesi 以舞者的动作为灵感，设计了一款名为 Waltz 的衣架系统。它其实是由多个模块拼接而成，你可以根据需要将它们延长或者缩短。朝上的圆弧很适合挂上大衣，你也可以在朝下的圆弧中放上围巾或者挂上一把伞。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070211573662yxC4WmLTKVGZ9P.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.83974359\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115736Kk05ANbmy67wVUTj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115737IhCN4lTRGxWE5iwF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}